  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 29",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Arya V</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stoney_Sept\" title=\"Stoney Sept\">Stoney Sept</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n327 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 22\">Arya IV</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 28\">Sansa III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arya V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 30\">Jon IV</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 34\">Arya VI</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>While the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a> stay in <a href=\"/index.php/Stoney_Sept\" title=\"Stoney Sept\">Stoney Sept</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a> arrives with the captive <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Mentions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mentions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_29&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG/250px-Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG\" width=\"250\" height=\"135\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG/375px-Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG/500px-Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_thereisthehound.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Arya and Gendry look out the window to see what all the noise is about - by mustamirri ©</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Harwin\" title=\"Harwin\">Harwin</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> about the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a>, in which <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">her father</a> defeated <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Lord Connington</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand</a>, in a fierce battle fought in the streets of <a href=\"/index.php/Stoney_Sept\" title=\"Stoney Sept\">Stoney Sept</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> was injured and hiding in the town when the Hand's army invaded the town. Many credit Robert with the victory, but the king always said that Eddard had won that battle.\n</p><p>Arya is disturbed to find <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> being starved in cages, and gives one of them water. Possibly <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">Karstarks</a> as they were searching for Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>, they were captured by the <a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a>. The northmen are guilty of rape and pillaging, and <a href=\"/index.php/Anguy\" title=\"Anguy\">Anguy</a> puts the survivors out of their misery.\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a> spend the night at the <a href=\"/index.php/Peach\" title=\"Peach\">Peach</a>, a brothel. <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> is propositioned by <a href=\"/index.php/Bella\" title=\"Bella\">Bella</a>, who claims to be a daughter of the late King Robert, but Gendry refuses. When an old man makes an advance toward Arya, Gendry claims to be her sister and warns the man away. During the night, they hear a commotion, and watch as the <a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a> brings someone as a prisoner into the town in chains. Arya recognizes the captive.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_29&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Anguy\" title=\"Anguy\">Anguy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bella\" title=\"Bella\">Bella</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cass\" title=\"Cass\">Cass</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greenbeard\" title=\"Greenbeard\">Greenbeard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harwin\" title=\"Harwin\">Harwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Helly\" title=\"Helly\">Helly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jack-Be-Lucky\" title=\"Jack-Be-Lucky\">Jack-Be-Lucky</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jyzene\" title=\"Jyzene\">Jyzene</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lanna_(Peach)\" title=\"Lanna (Peach)\">Lanna</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tansy\" title=\"Tansy\">Tansy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alyce\" title=\"Alyce\">Alyce</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Denys_Arryn\" title=\"Denys Arryn\">Denys Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> (Mountain)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dunsen\" title=\"Dunsen\">Dunsen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Syrio_Forel\" title=\"Syrio Forel\">Syrio Forel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> (Kingslayer)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Leslyn\" title=\"Leslyn\">Leslyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Mooton\" title=\"Myles Mooton\">Myles Mooton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ilyn_Payne\" title=\"Ilyn Payne\">Ilyn Payne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Polliver\" title=\"Polliver\">Polliver</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rafford\" title=\"Rafford\">Rafford</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ravella_Smallwood\" title=\"Ravella Smallwood\">Ravella Smallwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> (Young Wolf)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> (Mad King)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thoros\" title=\"Thoros\">Thoros</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tickler\" title=\"Tickler\">Tickler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meryn_Trant\" title=\"Meryn Trant\">Meryn Trant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wilbert\" title=\"Wilbert\">Wilbert</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ment